# Keep local dependencies and build output out of the build context. The image
# rebuilds the frontend from source (npm ci + vite) and embeds it, so sending
# these only slows the build and risks clobbering the Linux install with
# host-platform binaries (e.g. a Windows/macOS node_modules).
**/node_modules
frontend/dist
backend/web
.git
.DS_Store
